ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Ville-Marie (Quebec) ** CHANGE OF BOUNDARIES **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE VILLE-MARIE, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from Ville-Marie and municipality of Duhamel-Ouest to Angliers, Béarn, Duhamel-Ouest, Fugèreville, Laforce, Latulipe, Gaboury, Laverlochère, Lorrainville, Moffet, Saint-Bruno-de-Guigues, Saint-Édouard-de-Fabre, the unorganized territory of Laniel and the cities of Belleterre and Ville-Marie.
